org.wso2.carbon.identity.oauth2.client.authentication

Class PublicClientAuthenticator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wso2.carbon.identity.core.handler.AbstractIdentityHandler
      • org.wso2.carbon.identity.oauth2.client.authentication.AbstractOAuthClientAuthenticator
        • org.wso2.carbon.identity.oauth2.client.authentication.PublicClientAuthenticator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.wso2.carbon.identity.core.handler.IdentityHandler, OAuthClientAuthenticator

    public class PublicClientAuthenticator
extends AbstractOAuthClientAuthenticator
    This class is dedicated for authenticating 'Public Clients'. Public clients do not need a client secret to be authenticated. This type of authentication is regularly utilised by native OAuth2 clients.
